---
title: Tandoori Spiced Chicken Tenders with Garlic Rice & Cucumber Raita
description: Love 'em tender? When it comes to tandoori chicken, that's the only way to go. Toss chicken tenderloins in tandoori paste and yoghurt, knock up some tasty sides and sit down to a meal that'll make you swoon.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tandoori-spiced-chicken-tenders-5830d003.jpg
